{
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "description": "Operator view for the Prometheus-evaluated AI Gateway alert lifecycle. Alertmanager groups, deduplicates, inhibits, and resolves alerts; Grafana shows current state plus recently resolved state reconstructed from the retained Prometheus ALERTS series. No Grafana-managed rules or external notification receiver are used.",
  "editable": false,
